title: #72 - The TanaCon Con & Logan Paul vs KSI
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast Ethan is flying solo while Hila is visiting family back home. Ethan dissects the TanaCon fiasco, the Logan Paul vs KSI fight, Jimmy Lee's view botting, a Canadian crackhead falling through a ceiling, and most importantly gives an update on the grand Metamucil experiment!
